'''Philip Proctor''' (born [[July 28]], [[1940s#1940|1940]]) is an American actor and voice actor who has provided voices for several ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars video games|video games]].

{{Bio-stub}}

==Roles==
{{Mediacat|soundcat=Audio files of Phil Proctor}}
*''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]'' &ndash; [[Tomaas Azzameen/Legends|Tomaas Azzameen]], Imperial Officer 4, Rebel Pilot 7
*''[[Star Wars: Force Commander]]'' &ndash; Attack Tank Driver, Rebel Trooper #2, Stormtrooper Sergeant
*''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]'' &ndash; Empire cruiser captain, Jedi Master, Viceroy [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]]
*''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'' &ndash; [[Devar Gann]], Doctor [[Vernan (scientist)|Vernan]], [[Gon-Sa]], Master [[Nimi]], Master [[Orbis Keln]], [[Maverse Pontilo]], Officer [[Mark Vempor]], [[Orin-Va]], [[Tarkos Sund]], [[Vanel]], Zoo Official

